text: Eidskog is a municipality in Innlandet county, Norway. 6,032 people lived there (2022). A police station overlaps (part of) the border with Sweden; It is manned by both Swedish and Norwegian police officers; Swedish police officers are armed at all times (while in uniform).https://www.nrk.no/innlandet/felles-politistasjon-pa-grensa-mellom- eidskog-og-eda_-men-ulike-regler-om-bevaepning-skaper-problemer-1.17309184.
